Text: dude, pls dont do that anymore... rammstein is good music, not to be tampered with. i think it's a funny idea,but no... please don't mess with rammstein's music

Or instead of wasting your bloody time downloading the whole album speeded up, just play your Rammstein albums in WinAmp and use the Pacemaker plugin and set it to whichever speed you like, you can also speed them up without raising the pitch if you like. They cost nothing, and take around 1 minute to download, don't waste your tme on this download!
